These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-8-1::.
There 2 different types of food: onion, orange
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: sports, family
1. the person watching sports movies is on the right of the person watching family movies##1
2. the person eating onion is not to the right of the person watching family movies##8

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |    2     |
| Food        | onion   | orange   |
| Movie-Genre   | family | sports |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-8-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: juice, soy-milk
2 different pets are kept: dog, rabbit
1. the owner of the dog is not to the left of the person drinking soy-milk##8
2. the owner of the dog is somewhere to the right of the person drinking soy-milk##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2    |
| Beverage   | soy-milk | juice   |
| Pet      | rabbit | dog |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-8-3::.
There are 2 different favourite colors: ivory, aquamarine
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: pop, r&b
1. the person who likes ivory is not to the left of the fan of r&b##8
2. the person who likes aquamarine is on the left of the fan of r&b##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |
| Color          | aquamarine | ivory |
| Music-Genre   | pop   | r&b     |

 #################################

 
